text:
Coenties Slip, west side, north from South Street (left) and viewing across the low structures here to a backdrop formed by the various office structures on Broad Street. At the right is the "El" turning into Front Street on its way to South Ferry.

View 2 is limited to the corner buildings. Note the external staircase entrance to No. 22-3 South Street.

May 20, 1939
Views: 1 and 2

P. L. Sperr
title: Manhattan: Coenties Slip - South Street
